{"tid":15842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪分手刺人夫7刀    靚女學護判監3年8個月","createTime":"2016-12-01T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:43:58.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14c340e224d2adc5c7de9b5fe4fffe11a3db7149","tid":15842,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161201/large/1480576680_ed41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161201%2Flarge%2F1480576680_ed41.jpg&h=ee731824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29歲女學護戀上有婦之夫，分手後仍藕斷絲連，今年初在上水寓所及車上先後刺了男友7刀，又致電對方母親出言恐嚇。學護簡媛茌早前在區域法院被裁定5項有意圖傷人及刑事恐嚇罪成，今被入獄3年8個月。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指，辯方稱被告錯愛，亦被事主玩弄而犯案，法官在此無意作道德或倫理審判，惟被告拍拖前已知事主已婚，但法官都明白愛情令人盲目，被告與事主的感情不能和親友傾訴，後來更墮胎，相信被告承受很大壓力，加上被告之前曾經被男人欺騙，本打算與事主拍拖能彌補感情缺失，但事與願違。"},{"pid":"4f66ccdf75727adca5c640380b26b8d9811b6c40","tid":15842,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"依家先判？"},{"pid":"719efa5fcec21c98f8070f302eed607a293deb11","tid":15842,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160927/large/1474972241_08fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160927%2Flarge%2F1474972241_08fd.jpg&h=ad84c9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似盧斯達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff72953940d60e56fef099645d7e1111d9d58da1","tid":15842,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"請清洪打果單？<br />\nhi,風化影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dcba2c7da52652cd98bfcdc555f828f4f131c6","tid":15842,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:27:32.000Z","msg"